  "description": {
    "en": "Reaching pure performance without any cambers – the Matrix combines a locked-in racing feeling with ease of use. The race-oriented outline with a small sail head was updated with slightly increased luff curve, which adds tension to the sail to boost the performance even more. Small modifications in the shaping of the seams in the middle of the sail helped us to refine the profile, leading to a light feeling even when you’re overpowered. The relatively wide sail foot and the cross batten further enhance the power and performance of the Matrix, while it never loses its user-friendly and controllable character."
